      <title>XP的“英文-美式键盘”总是删除不掉解决方法</title>
      <link>http://fatkun.github.io/2009/09/xp%E7%9A%84%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87-%E7%BE%8E%E5%BC%8F%E9%94%AE%E7%9B%98%E6%80%BB%E6%98%AF%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%89%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95.html</link>
